-- MOVES-Adam & Co appoints four people to Aberdeen office
-- 
-- Tue Sep 23, 2014 01:17PM EDT
-- None



Sept 23 (Reuters) - Scottish private bank Adam & Co appointed four people to its Aberdeen office.

Louise Smith joins as a senior business development manager from Royal Bank of Scotland Group <RBS.L>, Adam & Co said. Ricki Garden joins as a financial planning manager from Anderson Anderson and Brown, while Monica Tonissoo joins as a paraplanner.